			namespace: term
			usage: term.NNN [options]
		</h2>
		<p>
			Where NNN (and options) is one of the following:
		</p>
		<table>
			<td>
				<tr width="100%">term [terminal_name]</tr>
				<tr width="100%">reset</tr>
				<tr width="100%">initialize</tr>
